highlights.text: “Believer” by Imagine Dragons has been on Top Songs Global the longest, at 321 weeks straight.
The Weeknd has the most spots on Top Songs Global. “Die For You (with Ariana Grande) - Remix” is the highest at #6.
“La Bebe - Remix” by Yng Lvcas and Peso Pluma is the biggest gainer on Top Songs Global, up 83 spots at #10.
“BESO” by ROSALÍA and Rauw Alejandro is the highest new entry on Top Songs Global at #5.
